## Design System — Monochrome Editorial

The entire frontend follows a strict minimalist monochrome aesthetic inspired by fashion magazines and architecture books.

| Token | Value |
|:---|:---|
| **Palette** | Pure black `#000` & white `#FFF` only |
| **Display Font** | Playfair Display — oversized editorial headlines |
| **Body Font** | Source Serif 4 — refined reading text |
| **Border Radius** | 0px everywhere — sharp, architectural |
| **Shadows** | None — hierarchy via borders and whitespace |
| **Hover Effect** | Black ↔ white inversion (60ms) |
| **Badges** | Monochrome: solid border = default, dashed = in progress, inverted = high/admin/done |

