## Features

- **Auth** — Register/Login with JWT, bcrypt hashing, session persistence
- **Projects** — CRUD with role-based access (Admin/Member)
- **Tasks** — Kanban board, priority, due dates, assignment, overdue detection
- **Team** — Add members by email, change roles, remove (with safety check)
- **Dashboard** — Aggregate stats, personal task summary, overdue alerts, project progress
- **RBAC** — Admin: full CRUD | Member: status updates on assigned tasks only
- **Accessibility** — `aria-labels`, `htmlFor`, `focus-visible` outlines, keyboard navigation
- **Responsive** — Mobile-first breakpoints at 768px and 1024px

